          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Savannah</placeName>
                                        <date>April 5/54</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>Philad</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">Dear sir</p>
                              <p>I recd. this day a order for a set of unbound Prayer Books at
                                        $15—<lb/> for a <persName>Miss Hart</persName> of
                                                  <placeName>Sav</placeName>= you<lb/> will please
                                        send them as early<lb/> as you Possible can <sic>allso</sic>
                                        a few<lb/> daily Prayer Books would sell<lb/> in hope this
                                        will find you<lb/> in the best of health</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I remain Dear sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">yours most ob</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <persName role="author">R Mayer</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>P.S.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I would have <sic>send</sic> this by
                                                  <sic>stimmer</sic><lb/> but the order came
                                                  <sic>to</sic> late</p>
                    </body>
